    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a thrilling odyssey through war-torn skies. In a post-apocalyptic realm where the boundary between technology and the supernatural has disintegrated. Take flight as the fearless pilot GHOST, accompanied by the enigmatic spirit known only as &quot;The Phoenix,&quot; as you are thrust into a relentless battle against possessed war machines and otherworldly monstrosities. Beautifully executed pixel art immerses you in this exhilarating, fast-paced top-down shoot 'em up! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Your Arsenal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Salvage unique loot from fallen foes or gather blueprints from the chaos of battle and exchange them for the keys to a formidable array of new weapons. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/f8f3c3d1a3227e788586413edf57454c.poster.avif?t=1771253626\" width=612 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/f8f3c3d1a3227e788586413edf57454c.webm?t=1771253626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/f8f3c3d1a3227e788586413edf57454c.mp4?t=1771253626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Night is Dark and Full of Terrors</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you dare to face the dangers of the night for the allure of greater rewards, or will you strategically navigate the daylight hours, ensuring a safer but potentially less lucrative journey?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/82656b03b8170a0f28115b99c1c66b96.poster.avif?t=1771253626\" width=612 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/82656b03b8170a0f28115b99c1c66b96.webm?t=1771253626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/82656b03b8170a0f28115b99c1c66b96.mp4?t=1771253626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Upgrades and Abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect souls from fallen enemies and unlock permanent upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/92767bee853e4d2628b5d83a7d6b282f.poster.avif?t=1771253626\" width=612 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/92767bee853e4d2628b5d83a7d6b282f.webm?t=1771253626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/92767bee853e4d2628b5d83a7d6b282f.mp4?t=1771253626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relics of the Past</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect relics of the past from Elite enemy encounters and unlock unique abilities or passive upgrades to modify each journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/e89ba5ef2633a56de7c0ef0b52c5c7e3.poster.avif?t=1771253626\" width=614 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/e89ba5ef2633a56de7c0ef0b52c5c7e3.webm?t=1771253626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195710/extras/e89ba5ef2633a56de7c0ef0b52c5c7e3.mp4?t=1771253626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
